  "original_title": "\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0db4\u0dd4 \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca CID\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0dba \u0db4\u0dc4\u0d9a \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A five-hour statement from the former president to the CID",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Criminal Investigation Department has given a five-hour statement from former President Maithripala Sirisena regarding the President's pardoning of a person named Shramanta Jayamaha who was in prison after receiving the death penalty.",
        "According to a complaint made by Ratana Thera in Athuli, an investigation is going on and this statement has been recorded from the former President in relation to that investigation.",
        "Shramanta was convicted and serving a prison sentence in relation to the Royal Park murder incident which caused a great controversy and the former President arranged for him to receive a presidential pardon."
      ],
